nodes.text: Fubini was a female Human who was affiliated with the reconstituted Sith Empire during the Cold War between the Empire and the Galactic Republic. Around the year 3643 BBY, she worked as a merchant inside the spaceport located near the Imperial capital of Kaas City on the planet Dromund Kaas. While stationed at the spaceport, Fubini wore gray-colored clothing and sold armor from a stall. She had brown hair, blue eyes, and fair skin.
Fubini first appeared as an Imperial armor vendor in the spaceport on the planet Dromund Kaas in Star Wars: The Old Republic, a 2011 MMORPG produced by BioWare.
